**Create an artifact**

curl --request POST \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk' \
  --data '{
    "name":"Artifact1",
    "version": "1.0",
    "ids": {
    	"external": "ext-id-1"
    },
    "keys": {
    	"external": "ext-key-1"
    },
    "type": {
        "key":"TypeA1"
    },
    "container": {
        "key":"KEY 1"
    }
}'

**Get all artifacts**

curl --request GET \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Get an artifact by key**

curl --request GET \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts/ART1 \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Get artifacts by container key**

curl --request GET \
  --url 'http://localhost:9000/artifacts?contKey=KEY%201' \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Get artifacts by external key**

curl --request GET \
  --url 'http://localhost:9000/artifacts?externalKey=ext-key-1' \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Get artifacts by container key and external key**

curl --request GET \
  --url 'http://localhost:9000/artifacts?contKey=KEY%201&externalKey=ext-key-1' \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Get a particular version of an artifact**

curl --request GET \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts/ART1/versions/1.0 \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Get all versions of an artifact**

curl --request GET \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts/ART1/versions \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk'
  
**Update an artifact**

curl --request PUT \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts/ART1 \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..jybnQyDLl5ZWnhHqxiFU6peX1zsq7ZzO7aKdIv54_mk' \
  --data '{
    "name":"Artifact1",
    "version": "1.1",
    "ids": {
    	"external": "ext-id-11"
    },
    "keys": {
    	"external": "ext-key-11"
    },
    "type": {
        "key":"TypeA2"
    },
    "container": {
        "key":"KEY 1"
    }
}'

**Delete an artifact**

curl --request DELETE \
  --url http://localhost:9000/artifacts/ART2 \
  --header 'X-Auth-Token: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..aBBv4LTK6O0OVfxu_qSWbLxFGOh9lFU5Hbyq2fcKlZU'
